🚀 Stage 2 — Production Stage

Now add:

FROM node:18-alpine

🔥 Why another FROM?
This creates:
fresh clean production image
without unnecessary build cache/files.
This is called:
🚀 Multi-stage Build

Note: Very important Docker concept.

✅ Add WORKDIR Again
WORKDIR /app

✅ Copy From Builder Stage
